reviews.name: Spiderman Collapsible Storage Trunk
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for my daughter bc she not only needed something to hold her toys, but to also compliment her new "Minnie Mouse" theme for her room. I didn't expect this to be nice of a product. I was able to fit 2 Laundry baskets of toys into this one toy chest. I will be purchasing another one!
reviews.title: Minnie Mouse Treasure Chest

reviews.name: Spiderman Collapsible Storage Trunk
reviews.reviewText: Bought this for my 4-year-old and 1-year-old's play room. They keep their play princess clothes and accessories in this box. Great for light-weight storage, since it is flimsy, but works great for us - exactly what I expected. And makes clean-up a breeze for the girls - just toss everything back in the box.
reviews.title: Good value for a cute storage box

reviews.name: Spiderman Collapsible Storage Trunk
reviews.reviewText:
I AM A MICKEY MOUSE FOOL/NUT, SO WHEN I SAW THIS ON EBAY BETWEEN 49.99 AND 69.99, I WENT TO WALMART.COM TO SEE IF THEY CARRY IT AND HAD IT FOR LESS. TO MY SURPRISE IT WAS ONLY 13.00 AND SOME CHANGE SO I PURCHASED TWO OF THEM. I THOUGHT IT WOULD BE SOME CHEAP FLIMY MATERIAL, BUT THIS IS A HEAVY BOARD CONSTRUCTION, ACTUALLY IT IS VERY HEAVY. I MEAN I WAS SO SHOCKED HOW NICE, STURDY AND COLORFUL THIS TRUNK IS. WELL, I WILL BE ORDERING SEVERAL MORE UNTIL THEY RUN OF OF STOCK.
MEO
reviews.title: SHOCKED AT HOW BIG THIS IS AND WELL FOR UNDER 14.0

reviews.name: Spiderman Collapsible Storage Trunk
reviews.reviewText: It was far better than I expected. I honestly thought i might get some cheaply made fabric with a thin piece of cardboard to hold the shape. Instead it was made with a thicker durable fabric. My kids love it, i got one for my princess and the Cars one for my son who is 2. Both of my kids have proven that these things can take a pretty good beating and still be usable. High recommended!!
reviews.title: 27 September 2012

reviews.name: Spiderman Collapsible Storage Trunk
reviews.reviewText: My one-year-old was needing his first toy box and we decided to choose this collapsible one due to the price and I must say this is a great little storage box. This product does not support the weight of anyone so it's exactly made to store toys or any other items. The design is great and it is easy to fold up should we decide to replace it with a sturdier toy box.
reviews.title: Great storage box
